  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A randomised trial with individual patients as units of observation will be carried out.
      Health coaching is used to modify health behaviour and thus improve disease control and
      health status, as well as use of health care services. A personal health coach is assigned to
      each patient and they are in weekly contact through telephone. The intervention lasts for 12
      months. No intervention is offered to the patients in the control arm.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
